Class Summary
ARContactForce A force model with impact, slide, and slide modes based on AR2 model for sliding, wavetable model as in ContactForce for rolling and impact.
BangForce A force model based on 1 period of some waveform (cos for example)
ContactForce A force model with impact, slide, and slide modes based on looping wav files Roll force is fed through lowpass filter.
ContactForce2 A force model with impact, slide, and slide modes based on looping wav files Roll force is fed through modal filter.
ContactForceN A force model with impact, slide, and slide modes based on looping wav files.
FilteredWavContactForce A force model with impact, slide, and slide modes based on looping wav files, fed through Reson.
KarnoppFriction A force model based on stick slip model.
StickSlip A force model based on stick slip model.
StickSlip0 A force model based on stick slip model.
